FieldSet.description: BIOSElement: CMDB Class that stores information about low-level, built-in software used to start a computer's operating system without accessing programs from a disk. A subclass of BMC_SystemSoftware, BMC_BIOSElement can be used to represent specific operating system and BIOS (basic input/output system) software elements in your IT environment. This class corresponds to the DMTF class CIM_BIOSElement.
FieldSet.label: BIOS Element
